shutil

built-in module "shell utilies"

- methods, e.g.
    - copy(src, dest) copies file/folder at source to destination
    - copytree(src, dest) copies folder, its subfolders and files to dest
    - move(src, dest) moves file/folder at source to destination
    - rmtree(path) removes tree at path
        - for deleting with backups, see entry: send2trash

EXAMPLE
import shutil

source = "main.py"
dest = "./venv/"
res = shutil.copy(source, dest)
print("Destination path:", res)
